videos.description: UC Davis keeps the ball alive with great hustle and finishes the play with a Lawrence White 3-pointer.
videos.headline: UCD's White hits the 3 off good hustle

videos.description: UC Irvine's Luke Nelson steals the pass and goes to other way to get the easy layup.
videos.headline: UCI's steal and score

videos.description: UC Irvine's Tommy Rutherford gets the offensive rebound and the layup to help energize the Anteater's offense.
videos.headline: UCI's Rutherford helps spark offense

videos.description: With 0.9 seconds left and UC Irvine down 50-47, the Anteaters inbound the ball but it gets deflected and time runs out.
